import React from 'react'
import {ProductImg} from './style'



const Slider = () => {
    return (
      <ProductImg src='/SLIDER_2500x.jpg'>
        <ProductContainer>
          <ProductWrapper>
            <Producth3></Producth3>
            <Producth1>MADE FOR </Producth1>
          </ProductWrapper>
        </ProductContainer>
      </ProductImg>
    )
}

export default Slider
